    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People in the workshop of a silversmith or goldsmith who create metal leaf by beating a piece of metal with special tools until the metal conforms to a very thin layer or leaf.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
